sets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:20:21.000Z","msg":"的確要打好基礎，一嚟就藝術好容易兩頭唔到岸"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"王家衞都係拍咗旺角卡門<br />\n先有鄧光榮肯出資俾佢拍阿飛正傳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:24:16.000Z","msg":"鄧光榮當年好多微言，不過唔係佢肯科水，真係未必有王家衛。香港其實都係要一個真正嘅電影大亨"},{"pid":"d864060e0bfe88a322a1cdac27e364a78ea13e0f","tid":1886510,"uid":278712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:01:52.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b73898562ff1ad7e96cbde8d8f05855761bd5cc","tid":1886510,"uid":98472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:27:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"221a190329731490adc12e23cde63d5dbec50f93","tid":1886510,"uid":202362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:56:38.000Z","msg":"我覺得李安應該算最屈機<br />\n李安可以奧斯卡都撈得掂（即係荷里活）明顯因為佢知道自己嘅優勢喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢嘅故事唔係一味跟荷里活玩法，而係將東西方文化融和。<br />\n不過佢係靠家庭三部曲成名，跟住再拍埋sense and sensibility直接入荷里活。"},{"pid":"6092f3cf054070749807fa9f689f6c3e2faf8ff3","tid":1886510,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:59:52.000Z","msg":"正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8434a90e379777f82b700d3225421204a70e3884","tid":1886510,"uid":174476,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T11:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三大影展：康城、柏林、威尼斯</span><br />\n特色：電影界最高殿堂，以藝術水平作為評選標準。相對黎講最為國際化，同時比較重視人文精神。三大影展分別係年頭、年中同年尾搞。同番制度上唔會令各影展重覆選擇對方入圍的電影。三大影展入面，當中又默認康城影展係最高殿堂。<br />\n<br />\n香港代表人物：王家衛、楊凡（藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n代表人物唔係得導演 演員都有好多代表人物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曼玉華人唯一攞過兩次三大展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n柏林康城影后 (阮玲玉 錯過又如何)<br />\n仲要三大展都做過評審委員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n芳芳姐拎過柏林影后 (女人四十)<br />\nDeanie姐係威尼斯影后 (桃姐)<br />\n朝偉係康城影帝 (花樣年華)"},{"pid":"0f663807c05ee4ffc0ef5cf5d3035e36d0ee2a2c","tid":1886510,"uid":174476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"221a190329731490adc12e23cde63d5dbec50f93","tid":1886510,"uid":202362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:56:38.000Z","msg":"我覺得李安應該算最屈機<br />\n李安可以奧斯卡都撈得掂（即係荷里活）明顯因為佢知道自己嘅優勢喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢嘅故事唔係一味跟荷里活玩法，而係將東西方文化融和。<br />\n不過佢係靠家庭三部曲成名，跟住再拍埋sense and sensibility直接入荷里活。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"佢連續兩部戲票房仆直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該暫時冇乜人會揾佢拍大戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2369aaf7e1786621664e452cd3b30791e4a1f27f","tid":1886510,"uid":202362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f663807c05ee4ffc0ef5cf5d3035e36d0ee2a2c","tid":1886510,"uid":174476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"221a190329731490adc12e23cde63d5dbec50f93","tid":1886510,"uid":202362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:56:38.000Z","msg":"我覺得李安應該算最屈機<br />\n李安可以奧斯卡都撈得掂（即係荷里活）明顯因為佢知道自己嘅優勢喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢嘅故事唔係一味跟荷里活玩法，而係將東西方文化融和。<br />\n不過佢係靠家庭三部曲成名，跟住再拍埋sense and sensibility直接入荷里活。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"佢連續兩部戲票房仆直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該暫時冇乜人會揾佢拍大戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T11:43:04.000Z","msg":"支持佢拍返類似家庭三部曲嘅片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418eb9e67732382ed560de12c339c87ffb8d599c","tid":1886510,"uid":13